name: Cinnamoon
additional_notices:
The following token has a variable tax function on the smart contract to change tax rates post deployment.
Do your own research and be careful if you are trading this token.

description.en: Cinnamoon offers analytics solutions that enable investors to make informed investment decisions in DeFi. Its DevTool platform assigns decentralized ratings to developers to indicate the quality of an issued token. The project goal is to provide essential intelligence for DeFi.
